des:
Media Push Radio is the best and fastest growing UK based online radio station and media network for discovering new brands, talent and music.
With a set vision to promote new artists, DJs, podcasters and brands to a global audience by providing them with a platform to shine amongst the greats, Team Media Push Radio also take the time to facilitate many of these artists, entrepreneurs, influencers and creative individuals with mentorship, management and consultation to boost their knowledge and reach within the industry.
Our team is passionate about music, entertainment and media and committed to delivering the best listening experience to our audience.
We take pride in being different from traditional radio stations, and our mission is to revolutionise the way new talent is discovered and promoted.
